:TITLE:
Medical Group Leader
:CONTENT:
}The Medical Group Leader manages the Field Medical Teams and the Medical Triage Team.He/she coordinates the first-aid/medical staff so that injured people are cared for in the field and the medical triage area.
:LIST:

Take directions from and reports to the Operations Section Chief 
on medical issues of the ICS.
Assembles appropriate Field Medical Teams and Medical Triage Team 
for the situation.
Coordinates with Response Team Manager on assembling and deploying 
the Field Medical Teams.
Directs and advises the Field Medical Teams and the Medical Triage Team.
Ensures that medical personnel have appropriate skills and equipment.
Ensures that the injured are tagged with a Medical Triage Tag and 
the information on the tags are kept current.
Ensures that all personnel actions and status of injured are logged.
